76
00:11:00,976 --> 00:11:03,351
Di sini. Berikan kami sedikit air.

77
00:11:03,779 --> 00:11:04,879
Baik, tuan.

78
00:11:07,583 --> 00:11:12,288
Semakin banyak arak awak minum, semakin dahaga awak akan rasa.

79
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:32,595
Saya tidur dengan lena seolah-olah saya pengsan setelah dipukul.

80
